OL,5, A poster for an Italian restaurant with
OL,6, Michelangelo's naked statue of David   
OL,7, has been barred from Glasgow subway.   
OL,9,FThe firm that manages the advertising  
OL,10,Fspace requested for the poster to be   
OL,11,Fedited to hide the statue's nudity.    
OL,13,FDRG Group, which owns Glasgow's Barolo 
OL,14,Frestaurant, said it was "surprised" by 
OL,15,Fthe response to the advert - which     
OL,16,Fshows the Renaissance sculpture eating 
OL,17,Fa slice of pizza.                      
OL,19,FIt created a new version of the poster 
OL,20,Fthat hides the statue's crotch area.   
